Package gudusoft.gsqlparser

Provides the class gudusoft.gsqlparser.TGSqlParserr necessary to create a SQL Parser and the classes a SQL Parser uses internally to handle different SQL dialects.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IMetaDatabase Deprecated
    As of v2.0.3.1, please use TSQLEnv instead In order to link column to table correctly without connecting to database, we need to provide a class which implements IMetaDatabase to TGSqlParser.
    ITokenHandle
    use this interface if you like to change token properties generated by lexer before send to parser.
    if you change a source token's TSourceToken#tokencode to TBaseType#cmtslashstar TBaseType#cmtdoublehyphen then, this token will be treated as comment
    you may also like to change tokencode of a keyword to TBaseType#ident, this will let parser treat this keyword as an identifier.
